Katana,by,NinjaMetrics,is,a,social,analytics,engine,that,measures,social,value,of,how,users,influence,each,other,The,Katana,Analytics,API,allows,developers,to,measure,the,value,of,social,contributions,in,applications,and,games,This,API,also,provides,developers,with,detailed,projections,for,the,outcomes,that,matter,to,developers,and,offers,the,tools,to,determine,how,effectively,features,facilitate,engagement,and,social,interaction,Moreover,the,API,documentation,gives,developers,access,to,send,JSON,directly,to,Katana,without,using,an,integration,library